    <title>NLP预训练模型的不可能三角</title>
    <link href="https://www.yam.gift/2022/04/15/Paper/2022-04-15-Impossible-Triangle/"/>
    <id>https://www.yam.gift/2022/04/15/Paper/2022-04-15-Impossible-Triangle/</id>
